    This is an simple api-server for a movie website

    Contact Support: Email: bang2001vl@outlook.com.vn

    Base URLs:

    • http://thunderv-2.southeastasia.cloudapp.azure.com:5000

    Authentication

    • API Key (apiKey)
      • Parameter Name: token, in: header.

    Code samples

    const inputBody = '{
      "token": "fugiat cillum esse dolore"
    }';
    const headers = {
      'Content-Type':'application/json',
      'Accept':'application/json',
      'Accept':'application/json'
    };

    fetch('http://thunderv-2.southeastasia.cloudapp.azure.com:5000/auth/destroysession',
    {
      method: 'POST',
      body: inputBody,
      headers: headers
    })
    .then(function(res) {
        return res.json();

        console.log(body);
